@SRodenburg I see. I was confused by the portal_instance name.
Defaults for these properties are, indeed, set here: https://github.com/cBioPortal/cbioportal/pull/7969/files/e805ff2f295eae71032d52dfcd754849a07a401c#diff-9be14d6564536099d9c431cf330dc2ad62abfecbbc191ac7c5814855dc37685eL305
So I think this three values can be simplified into one. As I mentioned, hg19/hg38/mm10 already gives you all the information given from the three properties that we currently have, and there is no need to deviate from the reference_genome property
